data.description: Looking for the ultimate lake home compound at Deep Creek Lake? Look no further, 387 Pinnacle Drive has what you are looking for! This property offers 6 total bedrooms and 5.5 bathrooms spanning through a 2900 sq.ft. main house and 1700 sq.ft. carriage house for overflow on the weekends, a paved driveway with two entrances onto Pinnacle Drive, a 3-car garage and fireplaces in each of the bedrooms in the main house for ultimate comfort. Each bedroom in the main house is outfitted with its own bathroom. Enjoy a warm evening by the fireplaces in the main level living room, lower level living room or outside at the fire pit. The Pinnacle community offers premium lake access and tennis courts. The community roads are great for site seeing and to get a breath of fresh air. The carriage house is unfinished on the interior with most major work being completed, just awaiting your finishing touches! Furnace system in main house was replaced in 2022. A tastefully decorated and well thought-out home. Whether you are looking for a full time residence, second home or vacation rental investment property, this property checks the boxes for all! Call today to schedule a showing at this premier property at Deep Creek Lake!
